<item>
            <title>[OAK-286] Possible NPE in LuceneIndex</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-286</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in LuceneIndex#getQuery(Filter) the first variable is initialized to null and updated to a meaningful value only if pr.first is not null, thus it may result in NPE when calling first.equals(last) (line 168).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12605358">OAK-286</key>
            <summary>Possible NPE in LuceneIndex</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
